			<h1 class="title">HIPAA as Logic Program </h1>
			<div class="entry">
				<p>The Logic formalization of HIPAA is a translation of the HIPAA law into a logical programming language, Prolog. 
				The Prolog translation can be executed and reports whether a given action complies with HIPAA.<br />
				We translate the HIPAA regulation into Prolog one statement at a time. You can verify our 
				translation by examining the side-by-side comparison.<br />
				We envision this project to be a collaborative open-source effort. The code base can be found 
				<a href="http://code.google.com/p/hipaa/"> here </a></p>
				</div>
